**Summary:**
This Japanese documentation explains how to use the Events Module in Amplitude charts, covering event addition (up to 10 events), default Amplitude events (Top Global Event, Any Active Event, New Users), wildcard search functionality with asterisk/question mark/brackets, and event filtering using Filter by and Group by with event properties and user properties.

